OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1775412669
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,CHorncastle
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a woman was found
OL,8,Funconscious at a property in
OL,9,FHorncastle and was pronounced dead at
OL,10,Fthe scene.
OL,12,FA 34-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder and Lincolnshire
OL,14,FPolice believe there are no other
OL,15,Fsuspects.
OL,17,FOfficers received a report that a 27-
OL,18,Fyear-old woman had suffered serious
OL,19,Finjuries at a property on
OL,20,FWarwickshires Way, Horncastle at
OL,21,F4.23pm on Thursday, 2 April.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
