OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1775412669
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,4,CHorncastle
OL,6,FThere will be an ongoing police
OL,7,Fpresence in the area while officers
OL,8,Fwork to establish the circumstances of
OL,9,Fthe woman's death.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Andy McWatt
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are at the very early stages
OL,13,Fof our investigation and are keeping
OL,14,Fan open mind as to how this tragic
OL,15,Fincident unfolded.
OL,17,F"Our priority is to establish the full
OL,18,Fcircumstances surrounding this death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
